Interface PredicateIntf

  • All Superinterfaces:

    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface PredicateIntf
extends MetaFilter, java.io.Serializable, java.util.function.Predicate<ValueHolder>
    An object-oriented representation of a query predicate that may be used as a constraint in a DomainQuery. Built-in criterion types are provided by the Predicate factory class. This interface might be implemented by application classes.
    Author:
    Jon Shields (cloned from Gavin King)
